room_title: Escape room "The Boy With a Bean" by Escape Room Wisconsin in Green Bay
room_description: You all have heard the story of Jack and the Beanstalk however here is the the rest of the tale. The Giant has pursued Jack to his cottage and has Jack on the run. It is up to your team to find the golden eggs, liberate the goose, and get out the door with the Magic Beans before Jack or the Giant return and find you!
